Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.22,0:32:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(636,632)}Jsi s tím smířená?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.82,0:33:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(618,630)}Omlouvám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.82,0:33:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tómo.
