Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.97,0:33:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Prosbu?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.51,0:33:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,O co jde?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.92,0:33:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,632)}Prosím,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.33,0:33:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,630)}chci být tvoje ango.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.13,0:33:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ango?
